                  "options": {
                    "html_content": {
                      "name": "Custom HTML Content",
                      "type": "html_content",
                      "default_value": "",
                      "value": "<div class=\"HOME_SEO\">\n    <h1>MB Part Source</h1>\n    <h2><center>Genuine Benz Parts At Affordable Prices</center></h2>\n    <p>We carry the highest quality inventory of OEM parts and accessories for all <a href=\"v-mercedes-benz\">Mercedes-Benz models.</a></p>\n    <p>We offer the full catalog of OEM parts and accessories along with diagrams to show you the part you are buying. Shopping for MB parts online has never been easier or cheaper. All the parts we offer are up to 35% off MSRP! and we are here to help. Please <a href=\"contact-us\">Contact Our Staff</a> with any questions you may have and we thank you for shopping with us!</p>\n    <p>Interested in Toyota parts? Check out our&nbsp;<strong>Toyota </strong>store here:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://genuinetoyotapartsonline.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">genuinetoyotapartsonline.com</a><br></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"HOME_SEO\"><h4>Note: Our shipping calculator is currently unrealistic for shipping rates on certain items. Please email or call to get a exact shipping quote.</h4></div>"
                    },
